        "description": {
            "name": "description",
            "type": "java.lang.String",
            "value": "I can not save large amounts of text. Error in function _stripQuoted ($ sql) function preg_replace (). With a large number of variables such as text 20 000 marks the last two functions:\r\n\r\n{code:html}\r\n$sql = preg_replace (\"\/ $ q ($ qe | \\ \\ \\ \\ (2 }|[^$ q]) * $ q \/ ','', $ Sql) \r\nand \r\n$ sql = preg_replace (\"\/ $ q ($ qe | [^ $ q]) * $ q \/ ','', $ sql); \r\n{code}\r\n\r\nnot work and return an empty result. You are urgently improve the error.\r\n\r\n\r\nexample:\r\n{code:sql} \r\nSELECT func_insert_category(1, 'example name', 'example text 20000 chars ...') AS res\r\n\r\nconversion result: \r\n\r\nSELECT func_insert_category(1, , ) AS res\r\n{code}\r\n\r\nand all this by the rules stripQuoted\r\n{code:html} \r\n\r\n\/'(''|\\\\{2}|[^'])*'\/\r\n\r\nor\r\n\r\n\/'(''|[^'])*'\/\r\n\r\n....\r\n{code}\r\n\r\nthe use of long returns from text:\r\n\r\n{code:html} \r\n<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC \"-\/\/IETF\/\/DTD HTML 2.0\/\/EN\">\r\n<html><head>\r\n<title>200 OK<\/title>\r\n<\/head><body>\r\n<h1>OK<\/h1>\r\n<p>The server encountered an internal error or\r\nmisconfiguration and was unable to complete\r\nyour request.<\/p>\r\n<p>Please contact the server administrator,\r\n admin@example.com and inform them of the time the error occurred,\r\nand anything you might have done that may have\r\ncaused the error.<\/p>\r\n<p>More information about this error may be available\r\nin the server error log.<\/p>\r\n<\/body><\/html>\r\n{code}\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\ncan better use\r\n\r\n{code:html} \r\n    protected function _stripQuoted($sql)\r\n    {\r\n\r\n         $translate = array(\r\n             \"\\\\000\" => \"\\000\",\r\n             \"\\\\n\"   => \"\\n\",\r\n             \"\\\\r\"   => \"\\r\",\r\n             \"\\\\\\\\\"  => \"\\\\\",\r\n             \"\\'\"    => \"'\",\r\n             \"\\\\\\\"\"  => \"\\\"\",\r\n             \"\\\\032\" => \"\\032\"\r\n         );\r\n         return strtr($sql, $translate);\r\n     }\r\n{code}\r\n\r\nand everything is working properly!\r\n\r\n\r\nRegards\r\n\r\n"
